# Component Organization

## Component Placement

- **Never place components in the App router folder** (`app/` directory)
- **Always place components in `/src/components`** directory
- Use feature-based organization within `/src/components`

## Directory Structure

```
src/
├── components/
│   ├── shared/           # Reusable components
│   ├── forms/            # Form components
│   ├── tables/           # Table components
│   └── feature-name/     # Feature-specific components
```

## Examples

### ✅ Good Examples

```typescript
// File: src/components/user-profile-card.tsx
export default function UserProfileCard({ user }: UserProfileCardProps) {
	// Component logic
}

// File: src/components/forms/user-create-form.tsx
export default function UserCreateForm() {
	// Form component
}
```

### ❌ Bad Examples

```typescript
// File: app/components/user-card.tsx (WRONG - in app directory)
export default function UserCard() {
	// Component logic
}

// File: app/(authenticated)/components/team-list.tsx (WRONG - in app directory)
export default function TeamList() {
	// Component logic
}
```
